In this edition of Jake HanTrendHan, Jack and Miles discuss the Taliban taking back control of Afganistan (and women), Dominic West playing Prince Charles in the next season of 'The Crown', Tim Tebow getting cut from the Jaguars, food preferences that say a lot about you according to Twitter, Amy Coney Barrett denying the Indiana vaccine mandate challenge, and Damon Wayans vs. Dave Chappelle?
